name: Designed In Italy
description:
A bold and unique premium designer Tshirt that commands attention.  Sex Sells clothing is a bold statement in mens fashion.  Confident men wear clothing that attracts attention and stimulates conversation.  Everyone else wears everything else. 

Designed In Italy is more than a shirt.  It represents heritage and personal identity.  If you are of Italian heritage you may not be made in Italy but you definitely are Designed In Italy.  

Every Sex Sells Inc. shirt is made of ultra light, soft and thin premium 100% Pima cotton.
